</div>      


</form>








<script language="javascript" type="text/javascript">

$(function() {
	$("#commit-request").dialog({

		}
	});

	  value: false

});

function startCommitRequest(event) {

	return true;
	
}

function innerStartCommitRequest() {
	$('#commit-request').dialog('open');
}

</script>
